OL,4,Cflooded fields
OL,6,FA farmer and a pub landlord say they
OL,7,Fare at risk of going out of business
OL,8,Fdue to repeated flooding in their area.
OL,10,FThe land around Short Ferry near has
OL,11,Fflooded three times since October,
OL,12,Fcosting farmers thousands of pounds in
OL,13,Flost revenue, while the local pub has
OL,14,Fseen a drastic fall in its number of
OL,15,Fcustomers.
OL,17,FFarmer Henry Ward says he is now
OL,18,Fstruggling to make ends meet due to
OL,19,Fthe frequent flooding.
