OL,3,CFarmer calling for compensation over
OL,4,Cflooded fields
OL,6,F"Crops ruined, livelihood ruined, it's
OL,7,Fseriously stressful," said Mr Ward.
OL,9,F"How am I meant to support my family,
OL,10,Fmake a living, with a farm looking
OL,11,Flike this?"
OL,13,FHe is calling on the Environment
OL,14,FAgency to compensate him to use the
OL,15,Fland as flood water storage rather
OL,16,Fthan taking the hit himself.
