OL,3,CFarmer calling for compensation over
OL,4,Cflooded fields
OL,6,F"Let's work together, lets do
OL,7,Fsomething pro-active and positive,
OL,8,Flet's use this farm to store water on
OL,9,Fto protect peoples houses, because I
OL,10,Fdon't want to see people's houses
OL,11,Fflooding," said Mr Ward.
OL,13,F"But we can't do it for free. We need
OL,14,Fa proper arrangement in place, and at
OL,15,Fthe minute I feel like the Environment
OL,16,FAgency are just lifting my leg."
