OL,4,Cflooded fields
OL,6,FAround 2,000 acres of Mr Ward's farm
OL,7,Fis currently flooded, but right next
OL,8,Fto it is a designated flood water
OL,9,Fstorage area which is currently almost
OL,10,Fcompletely dry.
OL,12,FPub landlord Rob Hardman says the road
OL,13,Fclosure in place due to flooding means
OL,14,Fit is not worth him opening on Mondays
OL,15,Fand Tuesdays now.
OL,17,F"My family has been in the pub trade
OL,18,Fsince 1955," said Mr Hardman.
