OL,3,CFarmer calling for compensation over
OL,4,Cflooded fields
OL,6,F"I was the first one to have to lock
OL,7,Fthe doors with (the Covid pandemic)
OL,8,Flockdown and that was bad enough.
OL,10,F"Now it feels like we've got our own
OL,11,Flittle lockdown every winter now," he
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"This part of the county just feels
OL,15,Flike it's been abandoned."
