OL,4,Cflooded fields
OL,6,FIn a statement, an Environment Agency
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "There has been no
OL,8,Factive decision to flood farmland to
OL,9,Fprotect property and we are working
OL,10,Fwith landowners to drain areas that
OL,11,Fhave been flooded.
OL,13,F"Given the current water levels on the
OL,14,FLower Witham, we do not believe that
OL,15,Fusing the reservoirs early would stop
OL,16,Fflooding of farmland in this
OL,17,Fcatchment."
